high_descs: Move to your left so that you are in front of the television on your left.
Pick up the credit card, on the TV stand, under the TV.
Turn to your left and go to the lamp in the corner to your right.
anns.task_desc: Turn the living room lamp on.

high_descs: Go left and turn to face the stand holding the television.
Pick the credit card up from the television stand.
Go left and the turn towards the right to face the lamp.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a credit card and turn on a lamp.

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the television stand on the right.
Pick up the red credit card on top of the stand in front of the television.
Turn left and hang a right at the wall to face the tall lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Examine a credit card by the light of a tall lamp.
